Big listviews can have in each row upto 3 colums: Icon column, Text column, Arrow/Info collumn.

Icon column should only have an icon in it. Text column should have one row of main text and up to two rows of explanatory text. Arrow/Info collumn should have either the arrow icon or a text (like remaining time).
Row column size is dependant on it's content plus spacing.

Setting information 1

System software and hardware information
This is the main page of the settings app. The most used settings from the status area are duplicated here with a gear icon below them that takes the user to another page for more controls.
More useful settings follow with direct control of their values.

Finally we have list items that invoke separate pages for groups of settings. A plug-in system is required in order for apps to be able to add their own settings applets. (For system wide settings. App settings are encouraged to stay inside the app.)
Toggles with setting gear below, that opens a page with more settings. These are the settings that our user survey found out to be more useful
